“Waah Waah Gobind Singh aape Gurchela.”
(All glory to Guru Gobind Singh Ji, who is both the Master and the disciple.)🙏🏻

Nestled in the Himalayas at 15,000 ft, Hemkund Sahib is where Guru Gobind Singh Ji is believed to have meditated in a past life. A place sacred to Sikhs and full of divine energy.✨

I had dreamed of visiting this holy place for so long, but somewhere deep down, I never thought it would really happen. And yet, Waheguru made it possible. Experiencing the snowfall, the serene trek, and the overwhelming peace. It all felt like a blessing I didn’t know I deserved.🥹🤍
